				  </div>

			      </div>
			</div>

			<div class="col-xs-4 blog-posts">
				<div class="thumbnail">
			      <img src="/images/compare.jpg" alt="comparison photo">
			      <div class="caption">
			        <h3>Don't Let Comparison Win</h3>
			        <p>When comparison kills your wedding joy. Don't let it happen to you.</p>
